long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you are fan of spacecraft shooter and survival games and like to simulate spacecraft shooter in for glory and duty, then Space Shooting is the one you should be shooter playing.
Alien Galaxy War is a fun 2D shooting game that you can play free online. Shoot all the incoming alien spaceships while avoiding bombs.
    In this game, you will be faced with an increasingly large number of alien and fight with 
many epic bosses in space war. As the game progresses, you will earn the right to upgrade your spaceships to 
bring it to full fatal capacity.

 HOW TO PLAY 
⭐ Use buttons to move and kills invaders. The spacecraft auto shoot.
⭐ Collect gems, items to upgrade and purchase new spacecraft.
⭐ Click button skills on the screen to active
